fields.name: Luxury Bed Frame
fields.description: Luxury handmade bed frame made from refurbished pallets, pre-prepared with treated and varnished wood. This piece comes as a 9 ft x 9 ft to suit large or king size mattresses. This popluar piece comes either a pre assembled piece or as packaged four piece self assembly unit.

fields.name: Lightening Bed Frame
fields.description: The Lightening bed frame comes as pre-assembled or self-assembly pack which includes a 9 ft x 9 ft frame to suit large or king size mattresses. It also comes fitted with wired tea lights within the frame which can be plugged in. This popluar piece comes either a pre assembled piece or as packaged five piece self assembly unit.

fields.name: Pine Bed Frame
fields.description: The Pine bed frame comes as pre-assembled or self-assembly pack which includes a 8 ft x 7 ft frame to suit medium to large mattresses. This popluar piece comes either a pre assembled piece or as packaged five piece self assembly unit.

fields.name: Diamond Coffee Table
fields.description: This hand crafted coffee table comes painted with a navy, off-white, light and dark grey design. This piece comes pre-assembled and ready for immediate use, combining two refurbished stacked pallets, creating plenty of shelve space beneath its designer top with 4ft(l) x 3ft(w) x 1.5ft(h) dimension.

fields.name: Mobile Coffee Table
fields.description: Durable mobile coffee table with wheel base for ease of movement between rooms.  This 4ft (l) x 3ft (w) x 1.5 ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly with optional flat or wheel base. This durable elegant piece offers plenty of storage space for those magazines or tablets as required.

fields.name: Stylish Coffee Table
fields.description: Stylish coffee table completed with a durable treatment and vanish coat, supported by four cast iron legs.  This 3.5ft (l) x 3ft (w) x 1.5 ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly. This durable stylish piece offers plenty of storage space for those magazines or tablets as required.

fields.name: Slate Grey Coffee Table
fields.description: This slate grey coffee table comes completed with a durable treatment and matt slate grey coat, supported by four cast iron legs.  This 3.5ft (l) x 3.5ft (w) x 1.6 ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly. This durable stylish piece offers plenty of storage space for those magazines or tablets as required and also comes with a central space for storage or display

fields.name: Classic Mobile Coffee Table
fields.description: This classic coffee table comes completed with a durable treatment and varnished coat, supported by four optional wheels at its base.  This 3.5ft (l) x 3.5ft (w) x 1.6 ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly.

fields.name: Glass-Top Mobile Coffee Table
fields.description: This glass-top coffee table comes completed with a durable treatment and varnished coat, supported by four optional wheels at its base.  This 3.5ft (l) x 3.5ft (w) x 1.6 ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly.

fields.name: Charcoal Coffee Table
fields.description: This charcoal coffee table comes completed with a durable treatment and charcoal matt coat, supported by a flat solid base.  This 3.5ft (l) x 3.5ft (w) x 1.6 ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly, with a central storage space

fields.name: Rasied Coffee Table
fields.description: This raised coffee table comes completed with a durable treatment and varnished coat, supported by a flat solid base.  This 3.5ft (l) x 3.5ft (w) x 1.8 ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly, with an optional wheelbase for ease of mobility

fields.name: Basic Coffee Table
fields.description: This basic coffee table comes completed with a durable treatment, supported by a four cast iron legs.  This 3ft (l) x 3.2ft (w) x 1.3ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly.

fields.name: Stylish Cupboard
fields.description: This stylish cupboard comes completed with a durable treatment and  a varnished finish.  This 3.5ft (l) x 2.5ft (w) x 4ft (h) piece comes fully assembled or as a pre-packed self assembly.

fields.name: Side Table Pack
fields.description: These stylish side-table pack come as a 3-pack, as seen in the photo, completed with a durable treatment and a varnished finish.  Each side table comes in the following dimensions - 2ft (l) x 2ft (w) x 1.6ft (h) and also comes fully assembled.

fields.name: Handmade TV Stand
fields.description: This well finished TV stand comes with four in built drawers, as seen in the photo, completed with a durable treatment and a varnished finish.  It comes in the following dimensions - 5ft (l) x 2ft (w) x 1.6ft (h) and also comes fully assembled.

fields.name: Handmade Wall Rack
fields.description: This multi-purpose wall rack comes with four iron wall hooks and nails supplied, as seen in the photo, completed with a durable treatment and a varnished finish.  It comes in the following dimensions - 3ft (l) x 3ft (w) x 2 inch(depth) and also comes fully assembled.

fields.name: Sea Salt Garden Bench
fields.description: This Sea Salt garden bench comes with built-in automatic lighting, as seen in the photo, completed with a durable treatment and a matt finish, inclusive of cushions and uplhostery, as seen in the photo.  It comes in the following dimensions - 12ft (l) x 4ft (w) x 4ft (h) and also comes as a simple self assembly pack.

fields.name: Classic Garden Bench

It comes in the following dimensions - 8ft (l) x 8ft (w) x 3.5ft (h) and also comes as a simple self assembly pack.

fields.name: Light Grey Garden Bench
fields.description: This Light Grey garden bench built with six refurbished pallets, as seen in the photo, completed with a durable treatment and a matt light grey finish, inclusive of cushions and uplhostery, as seen in the photo.  It comes in the following dimensions - 6ft (l) x 6ft (w) x 3.5ft (h) and also comes as a simple self assembly pack.

fields.name: Rainbow Garden Rack

The overall dmiensions of the assemby are 7ft (l) x 7ft (w) x 7ft (h) (including the triangluar bench backing board ).Note: it excludes the cushions and upholstery.

Note: it includes the cushions and upholstery.

fields.description: This stylish garden Table Stand comes treated and varnished with a matt grey and blue mixed finish, all built from refurbished pallets. This piece comes as a simple self-assembly unit. Dimensions 4ft (l) x 4ft (w) x 6ft (h).

fields.description: This classic garden table stand comes treated and varnished with a dureable finish, all built from refurbished pallets. This piece comes as a simple self-assembly unit. Dimensions 4ft (l) x 2ft (w) x 6ft (h).

fields.name: Classic Garden Table Stand

This piece comes as a fully assembled unit with a water cooler space in the centre for those summer refreshments. Dimensions 4ft (l) x 3ft (w) x 4ft (h).
